# Bite Bistro 🍽️

A responsive restaurant menu app built with HTML and CSS.

## 🌟 Features
- Homepage with food categories
- Category pages with meals
- Detailed meal pages with:
  - Meal image, name, price, serving size
  - Description and extras list
  - Customer notes form and “Place Order” button
- Thank-you page with animated testimonials
- Creative CSS enhancements:
  - Confetti animation
  - Floating food images
  - Emoji row and bounce-in headings

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Font Awesome
- GitHub Pages

